{"CURULE":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to a kind of chair appropriated to Roman magistrates and dignitaries; pertaining to, having, or conferring, the right to sit in the curule chair; hence, official.","pos":""}],"CURURO":[{"def":"A Chilian burrowing rodent of the genus Spalacopus.","pos":""},{"def":"Bowed; bent; curved.","pos":""}]}